description: OPEN HOUSES CANCELED. An exceptional smart home penthouse in the heart of South Boston. Spanning approximately 1,952 sqft and meticulously designed by award-winning firm Wolf in Sheep, this unit features two corner-exposed bedrooms, two custom bathrooms with radiant heat floors, and a stylish powder room. Outfitted with cutting-edge smart home technology, it provides seamless control over lighting, shades, security, HVAC, and entertainment. Soaring 7-foot windows fill the home with natural light, enhancing the open-concept layout. The gourmet kitchen, featuring Thermador appliances, flows into the expansive living area with custom built-ins and a gas fireplace. The dining space extends to a private deck through a NanaWall, creating a seamless indoor-outdoor living experience. Complete with two garage spaces, roof rights, and sweeping skyline views from Back Bay to Seaport, this penthouse offers a blend of luxury, innovation, & prime city living with easy access to Seaport and Downtown.
